guide : https://project-serum.github.io/anchor/getting-started/installation.html#install-anchor

#note for windows
please install gcc first, https://www.msys2.org/
then add PATH in environment varibale to C:\msys64\mingw64\bin\ for 64bit
if you face this after run "anchor --version" :
Only x86_64 / Linux distributed in NPM package right now.
Trying globally installed anchor.
then try to run this :
npm uninstall -g @project-serum/anchor-cli
